_aChangeLog.text: 1-added a Wall near the Hallway that Lead the T's to bombsite B
2-an Explosion will occur in Bombsite A when the bomb detonates, It does not deal damage to players
3-Added an Easter egg, figure it out yourself!
4-Changed the health of the wall that blocks the CT's way to bombsite B, it is now changed to 100
1-The Dustcloud now appears from Far distances
2-Added a Wall into the hallway that leads CT's to Bombsite B, to make it slower for them to reach it(The damage the wall can withstand until it breaks is a highly Changeable value)
3-Improved Ram usage and Performance by adjusting some Brush faces to "nodraw" texture
4-added some barriers on the T Side, You need to play the map to know the changes
